rupole deformation of the components of binary neutron-star systems in the\nlast few orbits prior to merger.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2009 05:21:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2009 04:53:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-29"}
